{"tid":918806,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"五台山之巔（OT：一生何求）","createTime":"2018-11-27T13:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T04:57:43.000Z","uid":72532,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"66761861fd2dfc4fd5ff3a01354b92cce8566f85","tid":918806,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五台山之巔（OT：一生何求）<br />\n<br />\n哪會再掛牽　紅顏一舉百千<br />\n誰寄盼永生不變　別了五台天<br />\n似親眼望見　誰也記得一些片面<br />\n剛足夠配飯菜共消遣　當真各有識見<br />\n<br />\n一些狂言　如折斷了布偶的線<br />\n善或惡說得深　聽得進卻太淺<br />\n一些閒言　如背上了最冷的箭<br />\n絕代美態會失色　瘋了　就當不可免<br />\n<br />\n哪會去說謊　何曾不敢見光<br />\n如對照世間癲喪　病了更健康<br />\n遠方有誰看　誰要拍低一些症狀<br />\n推翻過往萬句是空講　比虛構更虛妄<br />\n<br />\n一些徬徨　如昨晚已了結的案<br />\n恨或愛看不開　關不進某套房<br />\n一些情郎　如放棄再去拆的網<br />\n活下去也有方式　瘋了　是半刻解放"},{"pid":"82c7c35ed92fcd46396e2521d1793d9ce743ef2a","tid":918806,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875909e4327434f2a03df754d28eff2c19c826a0","tid":918806,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c7c35ed92fcd46396e2521d1793d9ce743ef2a","tid":918806,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c95c91e5109b949d424abe6e74f8a590481ab6f","tid":918806,"uid":41326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:57:03.000Z","msg":"善或惡說得深　聽得進卻太淺<br />\n好句師兄"},{"pid":"2ea1835f5d9f7dd2edfcc625eddcffcf5c9d3a0f","tid":918806,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c95c91e5109b949d424abe6e74f8a590481ab6f","tid":918806,"uid":41326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:57:03.000